from\": 1223, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"astronomy\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the mode of competition is not like the usual exams.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mode\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"the usual exams\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Olympiad is like the Olympic games where participants representing different nations compete for medals,\\\" Banstola said.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympiad\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic games\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"participants\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"different nations\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"Banstola\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Olympiad is more than the regular curriculum that selects talented and genius students across the nation.\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympiad\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"the regular curriculum\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1480}, {\"ngram\": \"talented and genius students\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1522}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It provides a platform for students to demonstrate their talents and explore themselves, which is different from the regular curriculum,\\\" said Suresh Bhattarai, president of Nepal Astronomical Society (NASO).\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1685, \"end\": 1691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohinder_Suresh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.50125135245203e-16, \"text\": \"Suresh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid